		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Mobile</placeName> <date>October 21 5612</date></p>
				<p rend="align(right)"><addressee>Rev I Leeser</addressee> <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>&#33;</p>
			<p rend="indent(11)">Dear sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(12)">The <persName>Rev. A. Ansel</persName><lb/> <sic>formely</sic> from <placeName>Liverpool</placeName>&#44; died here on <date>Sept 8</date> last.  I am informed<lb/> he has a brother &#38; other relations in <placeName>England</placeName> living&#44; for their information<lb/> I would <sic>respectfuly</sic> request you &#40;in as much the Occident circulates<lb/> in <placeName>England</placeName>&#41; to insert a Notice of his death in the next <sic>numbre</sic><lb/> of your valuable <sic>periodicle</sic>.  He has been officiating as&#47;<hi rend="sup">in</hi> <add>Hebrew</add> <add>&#8220;busosal&#8221; JE transliteration</add><lb/> in <placeName>Claiborne Ala</placeName> for about 8 months&#59; he came here to<lb/> circumcise a child&#44; was taken ill &#38; after 8 days lingering he<lb/> died here &#38; was buried with all due honor in our <sic>burring</sic> ground.<lb/>  His Mohel instrument &#40;all the property he left&#41; is in my<lb/> possession &#38; are to be retained by order of the president<lb/> as a memento for his child&#44; which is now living at <placeName>Buffalo<lb/> N. Y.</placeName> as <persName>Mr. Ansel</persName> informed me previous to his death.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I regret very much for not being able to remit you any<lb/> money.  I have not <sic>collecting</sic> a dollar since the last I <sic>remitit</sic><lb/> you&#44; the scarcity of money is very great.  the rivers are very low<lb/> &#38; not navigable &#38; country <sic>peapol</sic> cannot come to our city<lb/>  Business of every dis<add>&#63;</add> are all nearly sus<add>&#63;</add>&#44; but as<lb/> soon <add>&#63;</add> I will remit at once.  <sic>Respectfuly</sic></p>
				<p rend="align(center)">Yours Truly</p>
				<p rend="align(center)"><hi rend="underline"><persName role="author">B M Emanuel</persName></hi></p>
			<pb n="1V"/>
			<p rend="align(center)"><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>&#44; Editor of the</p>
			<p rend="align(center)">Occident &#38; american jewish <sic>advocat</sic></p>
			<p rend="align(center)indent(3)">&#124;<placeName><hi rend="underline">Philadelphia Pa</hi></placeName></p>
